ial writings.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 4aArea Studies : French Studies. 4aFilm, Visual Culture, and Performing Arts : Art. 4aGeneral Interest : Poetry. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / French.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079147767040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791477670423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791477670/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles